title: Bobby And Eddie Challenge Seaforth + Eddie’s Major Problem With “Carrying Your Love with Me” + Elder vs. Millennial Returns!
itunes:title: Bobby And Eddie Challenge Seaforth + Eddie’s Major Problem With “Carrying Your Love with Me” + Elder vs. Millennial Returns!
description:
Bobby and Eddie take on new country duo, Seaforth in a game of chance! Eddie accused them of stealing the Raging Idiots iconic look. If Bobby and Eddie win, they have to retire the look. If Seaforth wins, they get to perform. Eddie has a problem with a 90’s Country song. We bring back Elder Vs. Millennial in a battle of Eddie versus Morgan2!
